This helm is made of a hard leather shell, braced internally. The metal face-plate affords additional protection for the eyes.

This peasant woman looks as though she has endured much, her weathered skin demonstrating the effects of a lifetime of hardship. A few pock-marks show where she has successfully fought off disease, and her face is hollow with hunger and exhaustion.
